{"tid":1446970,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［人手置頂］9月1日 全港十七區大集會","createTime":"2019-08-11T15:28:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T20:35:47.000Z","uid":304905,"like":71,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"34b3dea0d5ffc979255bb30a49db82ee34dcb1a2","tid":1446970,"uid":304905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:28:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1/9 十七區大集會</span> <br />\n<br />\n背景：<br />\n到咗九月大家都開學<br />\n人數會開始少<br />\n係時候盡地一鋪<br />\n<br />\n我哋嘅初衷都係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">全港一齊參與</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">守護好自己區 守護香港</span><br />\n而過去多次行動都有衝突發生<br />\n暴力升級唔適合和理非人士<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">呢個可能係第一次亦係最後一次<span style=\"color: red;\">最大規模嘅和理非集會</span>[/size=3]<br />\n如果政府咁都仲唔回應 我哋就真正要<span style=\"color: red;\">升級</span></span><br />\n十七區集會其實一直都有人講 但好多野要考慮 經過商討我哋認為係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">可行</span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">但一定要大大力推文宣 同埋要各區都有搞手認頭組團</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">目的：</span></span><br />\n1.真正做到遍地開花 各區政治覺醒<br />\n2.繼續追討五大訴求<br />\n3.和理非可以參與嘅各區最大升級<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Q&amp;A</span></span><br />\n<ins><span style=\"font-size: large;\">1. 點解搞17區？離島嘅手足可以去邊？</span></ins><br />\n- 18區-離島=17區<br />\n- 離島手足可以到其他區支援<br />\n- <span style=\"color: gold;\">唔搞機場！！（集中返係17區自己區 ）</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">點解唔搞機場下面會解釋</span><br />\n<br />\n<ins><span style=\"font-size: large;\">2. 會唔會分散晒人力？驚唔驚太多副本/支線？</span></ins><br />\n- 呢個大集會嘅目的係守護好自己區<br />\n- 單靠勇武嘅手足係唔夠 佢地已經日日食彈 <span style=\"color: orange;\">但有好多人都仲覺得事不關己 </span>所以一定要各區都一齊參與抗爭包括和理非<br />\n- 首先自己區嘅人要出嚟 <span style=\"color: gold;\">班狗嘅警力亦會被分散</span><br />\n- 假設真係做到和理非到時根本唔需要咁多前線人手對付警察<br />\n-會多咗一班淨係去自己區嘅人出嚟例如老友記同埋對衝突感到有包袱嘅人參與<br />\n<br />\n<ins><span style=\"font-size: large;\">3. 暫時可以點搞？</span></ins><br />\n- <span style=\"color: pink;\">首先各區要有admin認頭/入紙</span><br />\n- 整17區地圖 再決定邊啲區唔會搞 保障市民嘅安全以免裏外受敵<br />\n- 大肆宣傳守護好自己區嘅活動 就算路過都有食TG嘅機會 出個街都會俾人拉 各區居民都唔可以坐視不理 大家喺自己區都熟路 <strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">be water</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<ins><span style=\"font-size: large;\">4. 點解集會唔係遊行？</span></ins><br />\n- 因為集會比較<span style=\"color: gold;\">安全和理非</span><br />\n- 遊行宜家比較難拎到不反<br />\n<br />\n<ins><span style=\"font-size: large;\">5. 點解我地要硬推<span style=\"color: pink;\">和理非集會</span>？</span></ins><br />\n- 因為要儲人數令到政府同人民知道仲有人支持我哋<br />\n- 可以令到怕遊行有衝擊既人加入集會<br />\n- 到時無分和理非或勇武 只分前中線後援 互相幫助<br />\n<br />\n<ins><span style=\"font-size: large;\">6. 點解唔直接搞機場？</span></ins><br />\n- 首先機場已經喺8月搞咗3日接機活動 某程度上有得國際關注 但當日大家都見到我地嘅人力都集中喺機場 如果91當日再搞 十七區嘅人力就真正被分薄 所以離島嘅手足請到其他區支援<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><ins>嚟緊要/會做嘅野：</ins></span><br />\n1. 推9月1 十七區<br />\n2. 搵人認頭搞不反/17區admin各自組團<br />\n3. 整地圖路線<br />\n4. 文宣出圖[/orange]<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">831大遊行 91各區集會 92三罷</span></strong></span><br />\n搞得成對香港影響更大<br />\n十七區集會仲係籌備階段 我地已經聯絡緊各大公海admin同85七區集會搞手<br />\n大家有咩意見都可以一齊討論下<br />\n<br />\n我地要喚醒<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>香港人嘅政治意識 </strong></span>自己香港自己救 <span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">已經有幾百位義士俾人拉咗 而我地嘅五大訴求仲未得到回應 一定要全港都一齊追討我地嘅訴求</span></span><br />\n<br />\n十七區公海 link: <a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/C8zZIRSwF39SFKlLlBvc0g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FC8zZIRSwF39SFKlLlBvc0g&d=rP1lJsqA2sO3Td0%2BA1LJ54oeW3mBCvqo%2FKk1k%2BmNMw8%3D&h=ae58f40c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/C8zZIRSwF39SFKlLlBvc0g</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">十七區如下：<br />\n<br />\n  香港<br />\n<br />\n  中西區<br />\n  東區<br />\n  南區<br />\n  灣仔區<br />\n<br />\n  九龍<br />\n<br />\n  九龍城區<br />\n  觀塘區<br />\n  深水埗區<br />\n  黃大仙區<br />\n  油尖旺區<br />\n<br />\n  新界<br />\n<br />\n  葵青區<br />\n  北區<br />\n  西貢區<br />\n  沙田區<br />\n  大埔區<br />\n  荃灣區<br />\n  屯門區<br />\n  元朗區<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span></span>"},{"pid":"c3e401949b92d60687a9fc85bd9c9daf03ba5922","tid":1446970,"uid":48220,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:29:26.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一連三日有得諗"},{"pid":"6e3813293587711a640dc7e8acb154733d11c1a9","tid":1446970,"uid":203019,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:29:34.000Z","msg":"仲9月1? 會唔會太遲?"},{"pid":"152a994a4cb424052665c480ce8fbb87486ccfe8","tid":1446970,"uid":100495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:29:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5e4e9558ea0188b8096b21a419d7671a55a3f71b","tid":1446970,"uid":219152,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:30:19.000Z","msg":"搞得過<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a07b8dca714b1f86767614d04154ce75e2fb03a9","tid":1446970,"uid":295563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:30:32.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"925572559dac5a27bcca452c1e65aef8be90e2ab","tid":1446970,"uid":252374,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:31:09.000Z","msg":"五大訴求 缺一不可"},{"pid":"75d1b11cc049118b182e912e7f0b7c335fdd5936","tid":1446970,"uid":216390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:31:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbea9257f365dcf440fc7844c470bbe73db918a3","tid":1446970,"uid":4822